{"tid":33800,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"好想養哥基..但又唔想買","createTime":"2016-12-11T05:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T05:22:53.000Z","uid":63210,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b05648171fcd28cf256bc645b212e130f582a683","tid":33800,"uid":63210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:18:54.000Z","msg":"如題。<br />\n由細到大都好鍾意哥基，youtube ig facebook基本上都係哥基紀錄。<br />\n知道petshop既恐怖，唔想助長，但身邊冇養狗fd, 領養哥基又難，難道買哥基係唯一方法？<br />\n(類似前幾日有關ching的柴犬post)<br />\n利申: 支持領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />知道養狗講緣份"},{"pid":"cd25efed374b9a873ed15164f84acdea5ff93e38","tid":33800,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推<br />\n鍾意pug 多啲"},{"pid":"0bf8f0225a4e5b9e62835fcee37f6cdf4cf19710","tid":33800,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:24:50.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n鐘意貓多啲"},{"pid":"f144091f1a097a405aa4d3bc5745da40db6428af","tid":33800,"uid":4531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:26:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3a35d787474a5ed72c575e1be543ef5cac00baf","tid":33800,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:34:10.000Z","msg":"大屁屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c653ccc1bc55b408624b11e2c3c7dd3c329de490","tid":33800,"uid":837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:34:59.000Z","msg":"ching你老母"},{"pid":"4e359782f18577a8c3d820b4133077c4bc83a30a","tid":33800,"uid":46325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哥基係好難搵"},{"pid":"929019ef99ebeb5955bb0ff9efbbd881f2c35697","tid":33800,"uid":22838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:42:47.000Z","msg":"利申 無知<img src=\"/a