n利申經常接觸動物方面既機構</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好有愛 多謝您"},{"pid":"7b0f18316ed2e5659fe1594de4383a4c214106bf","tid":33800,"uid":63210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:49:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實搵 breeder 會唔會好過 pet shop <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實唔係好清楚咩係breeder<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9778d54786d71b29cc2951698d3b8ed0975be83","tid":33800,"uid":24607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:53:45.000Z","msg":"你唔覺得想擁有某個品種嘅心態有少少扭曲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2a60fe362dab6d5df572d3d3e01217ffea3dde","tid":33800,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:57:46.000Z","msg":"狗好撚臭"},{"pid":"ba00d5a7493c35496558f29815e13be6ab3a3426","tid":33800,"uid":63210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:10:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔覺得想擁有某個品種嘅心態有少少扭曲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都明白有個矛盾係到，如果真心鍾意狗應該咩種類都會去養。<br />\n不過，我係因為愛上哥基在先，再對狗仔同養狗有興趣，假設一生只可以養一次狗，我就會揀哥基。"},{"pid":"bffc20542e5d083cbee89a378e9e700f856676cf","tid":33800,"uid":49918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:14:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95d5ca14dedf26a220f7463fe5841d33a7f39a33","tid":33800,"uid":31257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:06:03.000Z","msg":"樓上巴打講elsa我都有睇開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以提早講定要留尾<br />\n但有時會覺得狗爸/媽好慘<br />\n生完就的走佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b6eae5c32218134bd24aba4fd843481a7773b3","tid":33800,"uid":5309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:16:56.000Z","msg":"支持領養呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我隻哥基都係領養咖，你留意下Facebook corgi club page 好多時見到有領養post!<br />\n不過要注意番哥基依啲純種狗好多病，同埋性格好痴身，有時會特登發脾氣激你，所以真係要有時間同資源先好養。 <br />\n<br />\n利申 當時領養左半年發現佢有抽筋問題 睇過好多次同好多個醫生 現時情況穩定 不過都久唔久會病發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我真係好愛呢個小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/12/000854_d3ed1775959e63a0015a2a8e07eba905.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F12%2F000854_d3ed1775959e63a0015a2a8e07eba905.jpg&h=c773581f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d30eca4ab48b18b5c5ed5a681e1a262fd9d1498","tid":33800,"uid":5309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Jf82z4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Jf82z4.jpg&h=17293caf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n訓教會訓到好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jx7DGu5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjx7DGu5.jpg&h=e6fc3c3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n要幫佢執屎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1OB20a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1OB20a5.jpg&h=bb02c4f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過望住佢訓到咁冧就好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XXmD24U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXXmD24U.jpg&h=c014bc9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地又聰明又喂食 做錯事後又知衰 隻耳仔後到<br />\n不過佢地認錯氹番你好頂引<br />\n佢曳到咬爛過passport, 100蚊, 八達通, 無限次偷食<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/12/002440_d37fa18ea6ebe8fa9a973787e81500bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F12%2F002440_d37fa18ea6ebe8fa9a973787e81500bc.jpg&h=0539e27f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c90180e35de076e29fc07bf54d9e5964bc964784","tid":33800,"uid":11261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:33:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Jf82z4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Jf82z4.jpg&h=17293caf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n訓教會訓到好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jx7DGu5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjx7DGu5.jpg&h=e6fc3c3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n要幫佢執屎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1OB20a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1OB20a5.jpg&h=bb02c4f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過望住佢訓到咁冧就好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XXmD24U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXXmD24U.jpg&h=c014bc9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地又聰明又喂食 做錯事後又知衰 隻耳仔後到<br />\n不過佢地認錯氹番你好頂引<br />\n佢曳到咬爛過passport, 100蚊, 八達通, 無限次偷食<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/12/002440_d37fa18ea6ebe8fa9a973787e81500bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F12%2F002440_d37fa18ea6ebe8fa9a973787e81500bc.jpg&h=0539e27f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a56ec0b3fe5309d7485e1e954d029825734d807","tid":33800,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:35:08.000Z","msg":"領養時睇下邊隻狗狗親你<br />\n係就要啦緣份黎"},{"pid":"6c4ef32093953ce0571938784faabead8ae98b3a","tid":33800,"uid":16383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:50:49.000Z","msg":"樓上啲人睇啲唔睇啲<br />\n哥基如果切尾 大個會有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a4e558fe0cb80b201e6cadc1c51adeb1812b84f","tid":33800,"uid":16383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓上啲人睇啲唔睇啲<br />\n哥基如果<span style=\"color: red;\">唔</span>切尾 大個會有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"15f0241c62d8b1e82919cf0e9e7a90096bd541ec","tid":33800,"uid":38351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T19:07:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持領養呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我隻哥基都係領養咖，你留意下Facebook corgi club page 好多時見到有領養post!<br />\n不過要注意番哥基依啲純種狗好多病，同埋性格好痴身，有時會特登發脾氣激你，所以真係要有時間同資源先好養。 <br />\n<br />\n利申 當時領養左半年發現佢有抽筋問題 睇過好多次同好多個醫生 現時情況穩定 不過都久唔久會病發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我真係好愛呢個小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/12/000854_d3ed1775959e63a0015a2a8e07eba905.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F12%2F000854_d3ed1775959e63a0015a2a8e07eba905.jpg&h=c773581f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger <br />\n之前有考慮過哥基，但後來睇外國介紹狗品種網站，瞭解多少少覺得自己handle唔到就唔敢養喇。<br />\n考慮因素: <br />\n1, 哥基有2層毛，所以沖涼後吹乾最好用專用吹毛機。而且我有鼻敏感，層底毛較幼，我會勁辛苦<br />\n2, 運動量大，最好每日跑步一個鐘。自問做唔到<br />\n3, 背部長腳短，易有關節問題。避免行樓梯同要有心理準備7 成機會中老年要做手術<br />\n樓主，請你養之前瞭解多啲。否則日後先知無預算無心理準備，人狗都辛苦。"},{"pid":"2560572fd385b11467936b751f7a9ce662b3d6e9","tid":33800,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/13/030121_c2bb29257e6ad816a0d6fd8e5c9d09bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F13%2F030121_c2bb29257e6ad816a0d6fd8e5c9d09bb.jpg&h=4a9f5b6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf87976f0c5877103cddad287296a06cec6e8577","tid":33800,"uid":53602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T20:17:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓上啲人睇啲唔睇啲<br />\n哥基如果切尾 大個會有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但就係人逼啲狗近親繁殖先搞到有缺陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然腳短好可愛，但對隻狗嚟講好慘，老咗就關節痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8fe77320e6575f74f1577ee0e75cdcaa06e5ca","tid":33800,"uid":13897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T20:39:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你唔覺得想擁有某個品種嘅心態有少少扭曲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都明白有個矛盾係到，如果真心鍾意狗應該咩種類都會去養。<br />\n不過，我係因為愛上哥基在先，再對狗仔同養狗有興趣，假設一生只可以養一次狗，我就會揀哥基。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家去到鍾意某個品種既狗想擁有都變成心態扭曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ca30d2ef66d0c13e70e570db26259503edf830","tid":33800,"uid":8935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T20:47:11.000Z","msg":"上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567b521682914d13625ec9927e2feba931207d24","tid":33800,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T20:50:10.000Z","msg":"屌心血少啲都唔掂"},{"pid":"23130b940079cccb5f785ffb2cde49cc7084730a","tid":33800,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T21:13:55.000Z","msg":"唔好呀⋯又惡，屙完尿一定踩到因該腳短<br />\n<br />\n養緊"},{"pid":"393a34db07de0783e229b28a4f76b53e6e72b8c6","tid":33800,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T21:14:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好呀⋯又惡，屙完尿一定踩到<span style=\"color: red;\">因為</span>腳短<br />\n<br />\n養緊</blockquote>"},{"pid":"12cc6eebd120262a241fbd30d11e37c6f16998fe","tid":33800,"uid":15580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T21:25:56.000Z","msg":"哥基真係好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d5b57602fd0ec32f41d1bf5cc67411e98bf731","tid":33800,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T21:31:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英國哥基犬數目激減  列弱勢品種</span><br />\n<br />\n英國畜犬協會指，當地哥基犬的數目少於300隻的門檻，因此有瀕臨滅絕的危機。隨著外來中小型狗隻的選擇越來越多，加上當地在2007年禁止，將哥基犬的尾巴切斷，令牠們失去一大賣點，導致哥基犬銷情欠佳，繁殖狗場亦減少生產，數目因而下降。<br />\n<br />\n哥基犬天生有一條長長的尾巴，但早年為了方便牠們打獵，令行動更加敏捷，主人通常會在牠們出生時將尾巴剪掉。部分狗種就連耳朵都不能倖免。由於不少人抱有「沒有尾巴才美麗的」想法，長尾巴的哥基犬亦變得不受歡迎。考慮人道立場，不少文明的國家，亦已經立法禁止為狗隻剪耳、剪尾以及切除聲帶。<br />\n<br />\n-----------<br />\n真係健康問題又會立法禁止剪尾？<br />\n其實有尾嘅哥基都好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf2d3d86bcc2cd9274a3350c3ab8aa3a1ce7f31","tid":33800,"uid":63210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:43:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支持領養呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我隻哥基都係領養咖，你留意下Facebook corgi club page 好多時見到有領養post!<br />\n不過要注意番哥基依啲純種狗好多病，同埋性格好痴身，有時會特登發脾氣激你，所以真係要有時間同資源先好養。 <br />\n<br />\n利申 當時領養左半年發現佢有抽筋問題 睇過好多次同好多個醫生 現時情況穩定 不過都久唔久會病發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我真係好愛呢個小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/12/000854_d3ed1775959e63a0015a2a8e07eba905.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F12%2F000854_d3ed1775959e63a0015a2a8e07eba905.jpg&h=c773581f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger <br />\n之前有考慮過哥基，但後來睇外國介紹狗品種網站，瞭解多少少覺得自己handle唔到就唔敢養喇。<br />\n考慮因素: <br />\n1, 哥基有2層毛，所以沖涼後吹乾最好用專用吹毛機。而且我有鼻敏感，層底毛較幼，我會勁辛苦<br />\n2, 運動量大，最好每日跑步一個鐘。自問做唔到<br />\n3, 背部長腳短，易有關節問題。避免行樓梯同要有心理準備7 成機會中老年要做手術<br />\n樓主，請你養之前瞭解多啲。否則日後先知無預算無心理準備，人狗都辛苦。</blockquote><br />\n有關關節痛問題，有冇養緊既巴打講下實際情況，哥基關節痛既時候會點嫁？同埋有咩方法幫到佢地(除左睇醫生)，例如運動？飲食？"},{"pid":"301ce23b28299ef0c44e84f543d12d475390fc5f","tid":33800,"uid":63210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:44:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/13/030121_c2bb29257e6ad816a0d6fd8e5c9d09bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F13%2F030121_c2bb29257e6ad816a0d6fd8e5c9d09bb.jpg&h=4a9f5b6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肥到唔想郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb3a24d32703aa6fb5d13e8037e64f9faae263b","tid":33800,"uid":2440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T02:01:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5e747248d58ea8d709ee3ab8fb05034f32491de","tid":33800,"uid":20747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:46:28.000Z","msg":"同女友都鐘情哥基 岩岩買左屋終於可以養<br />\n本身無養過狗 呢幾年不斷keep住睇養狗書<br />\n有無巴打可以提醒下點領養哥基同日常生活注意"},{"pid":"aa90c9b50d51e6e9c86827e17d5ea5c5f65add45","tid":33800,"uid":44037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b4065423b10b318e12749e6d775c8e5d03b96c","tid":33800,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,