ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T16:16:14.000Z","msg":"養西施，但都勁中意歌姬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Btw唔知oscar ma隻歌姬bb點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"5ffad474ed0a25194cc843a79f3ccbe14bbddc55","tid":33800,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T16:25:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支持領養呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我隻哥基都係領養咖，你留意下Facebook corgi club page 好多時見到有領養post!<br />\n不過要注意番哥基依啲純種狗好多病，同埋性格好痴身，有時會特登發脾氣激你，所以真係要有時間同資源先好養。 <br />\n<br />\n利申 當時領養左半年發現佢有抽筋問題 睇過好多次同好多個醫生 現時情況穩定 不過都久唔久會病發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我真係好愛呢個小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/12/000854_d3ed1775959e63a0015a2a8e07eba905.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F12%2F000854_d3ed1775959e63a0015a2a8e07eba905.jpg&h=c773581f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger <br />\n之前有考慮過哥基，但後來睇外國介紹狗品種網站，瞭解多少少覺得自己handle唔到就唔敢養喇。<br />\n考慮因素: <br />\n1, 哥基有2層毛，所以沖涼後吹乾最好用專用吹毛機。而且我有鼻敏感，層底毛較幼，我會勁辛苦<br />\n2, 運動量大，最好每日跑步一個鐘。自問做唔到<br />\n3, 背部長腳短，易有關節問題。避免行樓梯同要有心理準備7 成機會中老年要做手術<br />\n樓主，請你養之前瞭解多啲。否則日後先知無預算無心理準備，人狗都辛苦。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做手術個d其實養咩狗都預左第時佢地到中年-老年都要洗你一筆<br />\n輕則 5萬內<br />\n重則 10萬以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非睇得好開唔想醫想佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3233c5c80d5b49b9dd6c1dca03e9d56b241e6b","tid":33800,"uid":41255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T16:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" clas